quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf : yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah. Allah woondirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde nden, moftunde maanaaji e mo∆¥∆¥ere e barkeeji …óuu…óu…ói, wonnde ko pellet, on immintinoy on √ëalnde Darngal, fii √±aaweede yo…ìitee."
  50,2,"∆Åe saloraaki sikkitagol …ìe wonnde a fenay, hi…ìe anndi ko e goonga won…óaa. Si ko woni, …ìe ≈ãal…óu ko tawi kon Nulaa…óo jertinoowo arii …ìe jeyaa…óo e ma…ì…ìe, hara wanaa jeyaa…óo e Malaa'ika. ∆Åe wi'i: Arugol Nulaa…óo …ìanndinke on e mee…óen, ko huunde haawniinde."
  50,3,"Kere men immintinoyte si men maayii men wontii mbulmbuldi? Ngol immintinegol ruttitoo e nguurndam …ìaawo fii amen gaynude, ko huunde wo…ó…óiinde, nde laatotaako."
  50,4,"Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko leydi ndin √±aamata kon e …ìalli ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe, …óum suu…óaaki Men ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reenude kala ko Allah e…ì…ìani …ìe ka nguurndam e …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe nden."
  50,5,"Si ko woni, …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu Alqur'aana, tuma nde Nulaa…óo on ardannoo…ìe e mayre, hi…ìe e fiyaaku jil…ìu…óo ; …ìe tabitataa e huunde wootere fii mayre."
  50,6,"E …ìee fennoo…ìe ummital teskaaki kammu ngun dow ma…ì…ìe, ko honno Men tagiri ngun Men mahi, Men cu…óiri ngu koode …óe Men wa…ói e maggu; hara per…ói woo alanaa ngu ko itta ella e maggu? Awa tagu…óa …óin kammuuli On, O ronkataa wuurnitude maay…ìe."
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Men weertiri ndi ka ho…óee e mun, Men werlii e mayri pelle ko tabintina ndi, Men fu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji pu…ói e le…ó…óe woo…óu…óe."
  50,8,"Men tagiri …óum fow, ko wana teskuya waaju kala jeyaa…óo ruttoray…óo ka Joomi mun …óoftaare."
  50,9,"Men jippini kadi ndiyam keew…óam barke e mo∆¥∆¥ere ka kammu, Men fu…óiniri …óam gese e gabbe so√±etee…óe ekw."
  50,10,"Men fu…óiniri …óam kadi le…ó…óe tamaro juutu…óe toowu…óe, wondu…óe e piindi fawondirndi."
  50,11,"Men fu…óiniri …óam …óin …óon fow: fii arsike jeyaa…ìe …ìen, ka …ìe wuura. Men wuurnitiri …óam kadi leydi yoorundi ndi alaa pu…ói. Ko wano Men wuurnitiri non leydi yoorundi ndin …óam ndiyam, ko non Men wuurnitirta maay…ìe …ìen, …ìe yalta e gennale …óen hi…ìe wuuri."
  50,12,"Ado …ìee fennoo…ìe …ìe …óoo an Nulaa…óo, hari yim…ìe goo fenniino Annabaa…ìe mun : Yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen, e yim…ìe ∆Åunndu …ìen e Samuuda'en fow fennuno."
  50,13,"Aadi'en kadi fenni, e Fir'awna e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen."
  50,14,"yim…ìe Su'aybu e Yim…ìe Tubba Laam…óo Yaman …ìe fof pennii nulaa…ìe Alla …ìe O nuli …ìe, tabiti e mum en ko Alla fodani …ìe e lepte."
  50,15,"Kere Men ronkuno tagugol ka arannde, sakko Men ronka fii immintingol on? Ko woni kam…ìe, hi…ìe e ji…ìaare fii tagu hesu, …ìaawo …ìe tageede ka laawol aranol."